OL,5, A loophole allowing retailers to give  
OL,6, free vape samples to children is set to
OL,7, be closed under government plans to    
OL,8, curb their use among young people.     
OL,10,FA new crackdown on vape marketing would
OL,11,Fprevent the "unacceptable" targeting of
OL,12,Fchildren and teens, Rishi Sunak said.  
OL,14,FThere will also be a review into the   
OL,15,Frules around the sale of               
OL,16,F"nicotine-free" products to under-18s. 
OL,18,FLabour called the announcement a "baby 
OL,19,Fstep" and said urgent action is needed.
